reviews.text: Great service, incredible sweet and sour pork .. probably the best Chinese food I've ever had. We'll worth the trip and the staff was very accommodating for us English speaking folk. Not sure when I'll be back but I will!

A very nice Hong Kong restaurant opens until late evening. The dishes are all really great and delicious. You have to try the shrimps with chrispy deep-fried rice noodles and sour fish which are their signature dishes. The deep fried pigeon is very juicy and taste wonderful.

Had an enjoyable dinner experience here. Heard raved reviews about how even chefs came here for supper after work, says much about the quality of food here. For budget conscious folks, can skip their signature salt baked chicken which costs 490HKD, all the other stir fry dishes are equally good go for around 100+HKD each.

Had our final night dinner at @juxinghome .  Another Michelin Star restuarant but food was so so.  The only exception was the stewed claypot tofu.  The sweet and sour ribs are nice and better than normal.  However the dining experience are marred by the crescendo of noise from all the other patrons surrounding you.  The audio onslaught assaults your senses.  It just overcome you and you cannot wait to finish your dinner fast so that you could escape from noise.  Literally, you need to shout to get yourself heard around the table.  To be fair, it was full house.

reviews.text:
受到他人推薦
趕緊打電話訂位
原本訂8點沒想到7點半就到了
裡面非常多人
外面等待的人也不少
店面非常小
坐的不太舒適
而東西就普普通通
比較好吃的就白灼手切牛跟蛤蜊蒸蛋
其他就非常普通
生炒骨(咕咾肉)做得很不怎麼樣
椒鹽鮑魚過老了⋯⋯
不算難吃
但依照這個價位不值得
更是對不起這米其林推薦的名號

服務也是很不怎麼樣
明明看到隔壁在喝零度可樂
我們點就沒有
說什麼被另一桌擋住所有拿不到
後來又送給隔壁桌
我們依然沒有

整餐吃下來一個人要299港幣
實在太不值

2019-01 第一次去，隔離枱坐左是但哥同秀姑喺度，生炒排骨好正, 尤其係D汁！
2019-06 生炒排骨保持水準  啫啫芥蘭 啲菜就淋咗少少 🥂

酸菜斑魚 龍蝦上湯米粉底 
鹹魚煎肉餅 芥蘭煲 乳鴿 白灼牛肉
米子蓮評價個！當然價錢有番甘上下！去之前！考慮一下
食到火滾。叫三個餸，兩個人等左半個鐘先有野上。叫左一隻乳鴿，一個鐘多少少先到。哥時己經食完十分鐘，叫佢cancel唔肯。叫埋單唔肯埋。痴線。
